   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Provide  Education to 143 Vulnerable Children</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The percentage of vulnerable children in Hoima district is 42.5%. Buhimba Child Care Initiative provides education to 143 children in Buhimba Hope Academy of this category who lack basic scholastic materials and school fees. Classroom space is also limited due to increasing numbers. Help us construct one classroom block and to pay for school fees and scholastic materials so that these needy children can remain in school. One dollar makes a big, big distinction!</narrative>
  </description>
